{"tid":786701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停職警涉強姦求還押懲教「因為可以冲涼」官：呢個唔係理由嚟架","createTime":"2018-08-20T06:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T03:13:51.000Z","uid":54373,"like":73,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"04b3450c4cb7239851a984599aaf8378abd66087","tid":786701,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180820/large/1534743151_5909.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180820%2Flarge%2F1534743151_5909.jpg&h=15050981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉嫌非禮女網友而被停職的毒品調查科警員，於保釋候查期間涉再於公屋後樓梯強姦另一新相識的未成年女網友，停職警被控強姦罪今於粉嶺裁判法院提堂。案件押後被告未有申請保釋，但要求由懲教署看管，解釋指「因為可以冲涼」。惟主任裁判官練錦鴻稱「呢個唔係理由嚟架」，下令被告須繼續還柙，並交由警方看管。<br />\n<br />\n身穿風䄛短褲的被告余俊鑫（32歲）今被帶進法庭後，曾數次望向公衆席上的多名親友，神色凝重。他於今年6月因涉非禮案而被停職，保釋其間涉於上月月21日在沙田一公屋後樓梯強姦一名女童。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：FLCC3658/18】"},{"pid":"53c6b410d995becefc7edc7f80e2ce48056c9bfb","tid":786701,"uid":131691,"like":178,"dislike":0,"score":178,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:28:58.000Z","msg":"強姦完要沖涼<br />\n好開心香港嘅警察有良好嘅性交衛生意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6742d6261f07d6531967d224f8039b520b250c9","tid":786701,"uid":58552,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"喂阿哥，星斗市民點夠你玩呀<br />\n咁識嘆"},{"pid":"4f71b9a83806d24623a36f681017123f51b7aefa","tid":786701,"uid":113626,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識玩, 知道班藍絲一定護住自己人"},{"pid":"8ea24a60c32e4dc7fe59f6582fcadd38145ea8b0","tid":786701,"uid":39200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:35:33.000Z","msg":"驚又死喺 LAN 線之下"},{"pid":"989928a16489d4230a6b5f9817f0cfbed0ed99df","tid":786701,"uid":165936,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"4f71b9a83806d24623a36f681017123f51b7aefa","t